The paper also discusses the flexibility and successful rate of the algorithms, which may involve system dynamics and control theory. Therefore, cs.SY (Systems and Control) is another possible sub-category. 

Finally, the paper may involve statistical analysis and machine learning techniques to compare the performance of the algorithms. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible sub-category.
